## Per-Frame Data Flow

```
World::Update(ts)
â”‚
â”śâ”€ [first frame or after RegisterSystem] SortSystems()
â”‚    â””â”€ Kahn topological sort on writeSet/inframeAddSet â†’ readSet edges
â”‚
â”śâ”€ m_Dispatcher.update()            // EnTT signal delivery
â”‚
â”śâ”€ for each SystemEntry in m_Systems (sorted order):
â”‚    â”śâ”€ m_ActiveSystem = system
â”‚    â”śâ”€ system->Update(ts)
â”‚    â”‚    â””â”€ calls World::GetRegistry()
â”‚    â”‚         â””â”€ returns CheckedRegistryAccessor(registry, decl copy)
â”‚    â”‚              â”śâ”€ view / get       â†’ immediate registry reads
â”‚    â”‚              â”śâ”€ emplace_inframe  â†’ immediate registry write (inframeAddSet)
â”‚    â”‚              â”śâ”€ EmplaceInframeEvent â†’ immediate entity creation + components
â”‚    â”‚              â”śâ”€ emplace_deferred â†’ push to m_DeferredRequests
â”‚    â”‚              â”śâ”€ emplace_oneframe â†’ push to m_DeferredRequests
â”‚    â”‚              â”śâ”€ EmplaceEvent     â†’ push to m_DeferredRequests
â”‚    â”‚              â”śâ”€ remove_deferred  â†’ push to m_DeferredRequests
â”‚    â”‚              â””â”€ destroy_deferred â†’ push to m_DeferredDestroys
â”‚    â””â”€ m_ActiveSystem = nullptr
â”‚
â”śâ”€ ClearEvents()
â”‚    â””â”€ destroy all entities with EventComponent
â”‚         (in-frame events from this frame, deferred events from last frame)
â”‚
â””â”€ FlushDeferredRequests()
     â”śâ”€ apply m_DeferredOneFrameComponents  (emplace + schedule removal)
     â”śâ”€ apply m_DeferredRequests            (persistent emplaces, removes)
     â””â”€ apply m_DeferredDestroys            (entity destruction)
```

